	   <tr><td colspan=2> I have to ask what level your grouping with.&nbsp;&nbsp;Low level tanks are mainly made of people that want to smash things.  For every good tank below level 20 there are probably 10 bad ones. It takes a long time for some to learn coordination, if ever.  I always assist the primary tank or puller.  In fact, my hot key includes a tag telling the group who I'm assisting so there is no doubt.<br>  Maybe it's because my main's a rogue, and rogue's are highly misunderstood.  I'm sure I've had to explain that I can't be the primary tank just as often as enchanters have to explain mezz protocol.<br>   I just started an enchanter recently so I know this hell is soon to come.<br><br>Dadiella Shadowtree<br>34th Rogue<br>Drinal<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Dadiella 55th Lvl ROG Drinal<br><a href="http://www.unconquered.org" target=_new>http://www.unconquered.org</a><br></td></tr>
